            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> deo Apollini Maio<lb break="no" n="2"/>rius Iuvenis <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><del rend="erasure">V<supplied reason="lost">ictorino</supplied> et S<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>n</ex></expan></supplied>c<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied>o [<expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan></del>] <lb n="4"/>XVI <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ias</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Der Stein schließt oben mit einer halbtonnenförmigen Wölbung ab. Z. 4 befindet sich unterhalb des Inschriftfeldes. Z. 1 (Ende): zwischen A und O eine I-longa oder II-Ligatur. Z. 3: Lesung und Ergänzung weitgehend nach Rupprecht. (B): Stümpel: Z. 3: [[[---]]]; AE 1990: Z. 3: [[Victorino et Sa(n)cto co(n)s(ulibus)]]; Rupprecht: Z. 3: [[V[ictorino] et S[a(n)]c[to co(n)s(ulibus)]]].</p>
            </div>
